# vhs tape — skill-radar README demo
# Render: docker run --rm -v "$PWD/assets:/vhs" ghcr.io/charmbracelet/vhs demo.tape

Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 520
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set Framerate 15

Hide
Type "clear && bash demo.sh"
Enter
Sleep 400ms
Show
Sleep 11s
